Class Actions

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.monash.fit2099.engine.Actions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Action>
    public class Actions
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Action>
    A thin wrapper for java.util.ArrayList<Action> that does not allow nulls to be added.
